  problem="Teams working with epics, stories, and subtasks expect priorities to stay aligned across the hierarchy. When a product manager reorders epics on a board, the child stories and tasks should reflect that priority shift. But Jira has no native rank cascading — each level of the hierarchy maintains its own independent ranking. The result is constant misalignment between what leadership prioritizes and what teams actually work on."
